data.description: Highly Desirable community of Liberty Chase. Beautiful 4 bedroom home with a loft sitting on over a half acre lot! Main Bedroom has two Large walk in closets, and ceiling fans in all rooms. Nice open floorplan downstairs. Formal dining or living room area with an additional greatroom. AC Unit Newly installed 2021! Fencing updated 2023. lot size which is 22651 sq ft or .51 acres. Security System included. Big open loft/entertainment area upstairs and 4 bedrooms. Super huge fenced backyard! 2 Car garage. Electric fireplace. Great location! Very spacious home ready for new buyers. Come on out and view today!
